Replace,urn:ngsi-ld:entities:E1,https://uri.etsi.org/ngsi-ld/default-context/T,REGEX(202.*)
Create,urn:ngsi-ld:entities:E1,https://uri.etsi.org/ngsi-ld/default-context/T,REGEX(202.*)


